Hi Mike,
 
Thank you for your time today.
In today's meeting, we reviewed the permission scan and noticed some errors related to the Network not being found and hosts offline. We also saw the job stopped before completing the scan.
We set the permissions and the activity jobs to debug. You will monitor them, collect the logs, and upload both logs to this ticket.
You can reply to this email to provide an update.
 
Thanks,
